{"tid":177874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國班蝗咁能勇猛既","createTime":"2017-03-29T07:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T15:42:29.000Z","uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66f1771cd5be0fc9907c22ccc88e2ed5f1a81154","tid":177874,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"又放火又煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國果班就上訪比人打"},{"pid":"bfd7868d2d2bccd628b37417c05fef1134ebe3fd","tid":177874,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又放火又煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國果班就上訪比人打</blockquote><br />\n去到人地地頭就開始勇武"},{"pid":"3bea401a77da256572f089f82639bc3a44bada79","tid":177874,"uid":23919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:13:46.000Z","msg":"廢話,因為係法國囉"},{"pid":"c86f6a9220c28b38f8534676c60321944f6dc5d3","tid":177874,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:14:14.000Z","msg":"暴徒？"},{"pid":"b87e01d26388c481d3a429b6446d73e6a0358527","tid":177874,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:14:31.000Z","msg":"法國法國有勇武中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db33096ae7eb71e47fa8f667836ba6c03541654a","tid":177874,"uid":42452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:14:47.000Z","msg":"中國人不嬲都係係人地地方最撚惡架啦<br />\n平時講咩內鬥唔排外<br />\n根撚本唔係唔排外<br />\n而係最強既敵人就係自己人<br />\n一出到國即刻係威係勢, 冇人擋得住<br />\n<br />\n所以中國人問題唔係唔團結<br />\n而係中國人自己就係問題"},{"pid":"c2e635b18fecc7e9f189b32db6e6132a1cc4377b","tid":177874,"uid":34602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:15:31.000Z","msg":"放心示威，不用擔心被鎮壓"},{"pid":"199c328cf4aab4d9f280c2000291a2ec4db1ee21","tid":177874,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:16:22.000Z","msg":"蝗不嬲都勇猛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係支那公安&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;普通蝗先無事發生"},{"pid":"591d18848744259e95c59a7f2f81a3fcd2fc46a1","tid":177874,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:17:59.000Z","msg":"Chi na公安&gt;&gt;&gt;法國公安"},{"pid":"2920fe4b60931fa8f655adee99cffbff1d2dc492","tid":177874,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:20:42.000Z","msg":"法唔法國法國班蝗咁能勇猛"},{"pid":"3feaa672beb9fd3a81fad77a9e529dbddcc83104","tid":177874,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:32:47.000Z","msg":"遣返支那"},{"pid":"8131d85d8c04ca41f6c0b416c92c07fce54e2499","tid":177874,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"法國警察 用警棍鎮壓<br />\n<br />\n大陸公安用 衝鋒槍鎮壓"},{"pid":"686e21ffbaec6125e94dc1916846ced55823d917","tid":177874,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:42:29.000Z","msg":"我發覺一樣野<br />\n中國人去到外國之後, 就連示威模式都西化左<br />\n<br />\n睇新聞<br />\n見到D 中國人 學歐洲人咁, 用黑衫戰術.......所有人都著黑衫黑褲 戴黑色口罩, 防止警察認人<br />\n好撚型<br />\n<br />\n反而有時大陸都會出現示威, 例如烏坎村事件<br />\nD村民個個著到成個鄉下佬咁, 完全無哂霸氣, 好似以前 義和團 太平天國 果D農民軍咁"}]}